de.rwth.i2.attestor.tasks

Class GeneralAnalysisTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.tasks.GeneralAnalysisTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnalysisTask
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultAnalysisTask, IndexedAnalysisTask

    public abstract class GeneralAnalysisTask
extends Object
implements AnalysisTask
    Implementation of most common functionality of analysis tasks. The complete customization of an analysis task determining, for example how state spaces are exported, has to be done by subclasses.
    Author:
    Christoph
